<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Home</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-rbsA2VBKQhggwzxH7pPCaAqO46MgnOM80zW1RWuH61DGLwZJEdK2Kadq2F9CUG65" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style type="text/css">
        .search-form {
            align-items: center;
            display: flex;
        }

        .user-slot {
            margin: 5px 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">PennBook</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
            <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="#">Feed</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="#">Chat</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/createpostpage">Create Post</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <form class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <input class="form-control me-2" type="search" placeholder="Search" aria-label="Search">
                <button class="btn btn-outline-success" type="submit">Search</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>
<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <h3>Friends</h3>
            <ul class="list-group">
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    Friend 1
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    Friend 2
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    Friend 3
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    Friend 4
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-9">
            <%if (posts != null) { %>
                <% posts.forEach(p => { %>
                    <div class="card mb-3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title"><%- p.creator.S -%></h5>
                            <p class="card-text"><%- p.content.S -%></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-footer">
                            <small class="text-muted"><%- p.timestamp.S -%></small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            <% } %>
            <div class="card mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Friend 1</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. In vel justo nec ante sagittis pretium.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <small class="text-muted">3 hours ago</small>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Friend 2</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Donec mollis nisi id tellus sollicitudin, ut iaculis arcu rhoncus. Vivamus sit amet mauris vel nibh porttitor bibendum.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <small class="text-muted">5 hours ago</small>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Friend 3</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Suspendisse commodo est eu dui laoreet, at eleifend ipsum bibendum. Suspendisse potenti.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <small class="text-muted">Yesterday</small>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Friend 4</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Maecenas congue, leo eu tincidunt aliquam, nibh erat consectetur purus, sit amet fringilla nisl felis at leo.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <small class="text-muted">2 days ago</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
